@JiskeyJasket JKDHSYDFHSJ. Whenever you say that I'm always like lowkey like whaaat I'm an inspiration? fjsdhfjd Your pixel work is inspiring me to get back into pixelart. Seriously. I'm so excited to commission you! It's funny you say that because (1/2)

Art became something heavy to lean on this past year, so I feel as though it's become more personal. Opening for commissions is difficult, because I am seeking to gain a positive emotional outcome from my art.
A lot of my old work had an eldritch, old gorey feel to it. I'm trying to lean into more pretty gothic skeletony style. Right now I'm kind of in a fantasy fluff kind of style that's more cutesy.
Funny thing, I used to be a horror-themed gore artist. I wanted to be like junji ito! Now im like. I wanna draw flowers, lol.
